16:37.959 --> 16:42.375
NO, NO, HELEN, NO,
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

16:42.375 --> 16:46.667
I'M JUST A LITTLE
OVERWHELMED, I GUESS.

16:48.583 --> 16:50.041
OH, UH, WE NEED
SOME MORE WATER.

16:50.041 --> 16:53.667
