IN ALL THE WORLD

17:40.792 --> 17:41.792
YOU DECIDE TO
STUMBLE IN HERE.

17:41.792 --> 17:44.208
WELL, I AM STALKING YOU.

17:44.208 --> 17:46.041
HEY, JACK.

17:46.041 --> 17:47.000
HOW YOU DOING?

17:47.000 --> 17:48.792
AH, YOU KNOW,
IF THIS IS THE SCENE,

17:48.792 --> 17:50.708
NOT SO GOOD.

17:50.708 --> 17:52.917
I GOT TO TAKE A PISS.

17:55.291 --> 17:57.291
SO THEY TOLD ME
YOU WENT AWAY
FOR A WHILE.

17:57.291 --> 18:00.041
LET'S NOT BE AWKWARD
EXES, PACEY.

18:00.041 --> 18:01.875
I WAS DRYING OUT
IN MALIBU.

18:01.875 --> 18:04.208
OK.

18:04.208 --> 18:06.000
WELL, YOU LOOK GREAT,
ANYHOW.

18:06.000 --> 18:08.583
CLEAN LIVING, MY FRIEND.

18:08.583 --> 18:11.458
SO, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR JOB?

18:11.458 --> 18:13.500
I KNOW YOU'RE
NOT JUST TAKING
A LONG LUNCH BREAK.

18:13.500 --> 18:15.250
