TOO HARD-CORE FOR THAT.

18:15.250 --> 18:19.166
WELL, I'VE BEEN
REASSESSING HOW
I ALLOCATE MY TIME.

18:19.166 --> 18:21.583
SO YOU'RE DRINKING?

18:21.583 --> 18:23.750
I'M THINKING ABOUT IT.

18:23.750 --> 18:26.500
