ABOUT TAKING A TASTY
DOWNWARD SPIRAL?

18:26.500 --> 18:27.291
OH, YOU'D BETTER QUIT
WHILE YOU'RE AHEAD.

18:27.291 --> 18:29.417
YOU'RE NOT CUT OUT
FOR THIS.

18:29.417 --> 18:30.750
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT? I COULD SPIRAL
WITH THE BEST OF THEM.

18:30.750 --> 18:33.542
SPEAKING OF...

18:33.542 --> 18:35.875
SHOULDN'T YOU REALLY
AVOID PLACES LIKE THIS?

18:35.875 --> 18:38.625
I, UM, CAN'T HIDE
FROM MY PROBLEMS FOREVER.

18:38.625 --> 18:41.750
IT'S KIND OF HOW
I ENDED UP IN REHAB
IN THE FIRST PLACE, RIGHT?

18:41.750 --> 18:43.125
WELL,
THAT'S BRAVE OF YOU.

18:43.125 --> 18:44.834
BUT YOU WERE ALWAYS
GOOD LIKE THAT.

18:44.834 --> 18:48.291
YEAH, WELL, I'LL BE YOUR
PERSONAL SUPERHERO, OK?
OK.

18:48.291 --> 18:51.000
UNLESS OF COURSE
YOU WANT TO SPEND
THE REST OF YOUR DAYS

18:51.000 --> 18:52.834
HIDING OUT IN DIVES
LIKE THIS.

18:55.667 --> 18:57.458
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING FROM,
PACEY?

18:57.458 --> 19:00.667
I'M HIDING
FROM THE SUIT,

19:00.667 --> 19:02.333
BECAUSE IT'S EVIL.

19:02.333 --> 19:05.542
BAD THINGS HAPPEN
WHEN IT'S ON.

19:05.542 --> 19:08.125
I ALLOWED PEOPLE
TO BELIEVE IN ME
FOR A SECOND,

19:08.125 --> 19:10.125
WHICH WAS FOOLISH,
AND NOW IT'S REALLY

19:10.125 --> 19:12.291
COMING BACK TO BITE
THEM IN THE ASS.

19:12.291 --> 19:14.208
YOU KNOW WHAT?

19:14.208 --> 19:15.291
THIS ISN'T YOU TALKING.

19:15.291 --> 19:18.041
THIS IS YOUR FORMER SELF
REARING ITS UGLY HEAD.

19:19.834 --> 19:21.834
COME ON, PACEY.

19:21.834 --> 19:23.000
I KNOW MOMENTS LIKE THESE.

19:23.000 --> 19:25.542
ONE PATH
IS THE HARSH REALITY,

19:25.542 --> 19:28.792
AND ONE PATH
IS THE COMFORTABLY NUMB.
BUT GUESS WHAT?

19:28.792 --> 19:30.250
IN THE MORNING,
WHEN YOU'RE ALL SOBERED UP,

19:30.250 --> 19:31.417
THE PROBLEM'S
STILL GONNA BE THERE.

19:31.417 --> 19:36.083
ONLY, NOW IT'LL BE LIKE
A BIG FESTERING WOUND,

19:36.083 --> 19:39.333
AND YOU'LL JUST BE
THE JERK WHO SAT BACK
AND LET IT GET WORSE.

19:39.333 --> 19:43.041
WELL, THANKS FOR NOT
WALKING ON EGGSHELLS
AROUND ME.

19:50.875 --> 19:52.041
IT'S WEIRD, HUH?

19:53.333 --> 19:55.208
THIS ROOM USED TO BE
THE OFFICIAL MEETING PLACE

19:55.208 --> 19:58.166
WHERE WE'D DISCUSS
WHAT HAPPENED THAT DAY.

19:58.166 --> 20:00.500
AND NOW
IT'S JUST A FILM SET,

20:00.500 --> 20:03.083
AND I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED THIS YEAR.

20:03.083 --> 20:05.583
YEAH.

20:05.583 --> 20:07.125
I WAS KIND OF HOPING

20:07.125 --> 20:09.917
I COULD JUST CLIMB
UP THE LADDER AND...

20:09.917 --> 20:13.667
MAGICALLY FILL IN
ALL THE LOST TIME.

20:13.667 --> 20:14.834
HOW'S THAT
WORKING FOR YOU?

20:14.834 --> 20:15.875
NOT SO EASY.

20:15.875 --> 20:17.458
YEAH.

20:17.458 --> 20:20.208
MAYBE I WAS GONE
FOR TOO LONG.

20:20.208 --> 20:23.917
WELL, WE'LL PIECE
IT TOGETHER BETWEEN
THE TWO OF US THEN, RIGHT?

20:23.917 --> 20:27.000
