THE BEST THANKSGIVING.

24:34.458 --> 24:36.208
UM, I WAS
PROBABLY DRUNK.

24:36.208 --> 24:39.000
YEAH. I KNOW I WAS.

24:40.917 --> 24:44.917
THAT WAS A JOKE.
