31:58.375 --> 32:00.041
IT IS BUSINESS
BETWEEN US,
'CAUSE GOD KNOWS

32:00.041 --> 32:02.417
WE HAVEN'T BEEN
BEST FRIENDS
IN A LONG TIME, HAVE WE?

32:03.875 --> 32:06.125
NO, WE CERTAINLY HAVE NOT.

32:06.125 --> 32:08.750
YOU WANNA KNOW WHY
WE'RE NOT FRIENDS, PACE?

32:08.750 --> 32:10.250
IT'S NOT BECAUSE
OF WHAT HAPPENED WITH JOEY,

32:10.250 --> 32:12.583
EVEN THOUGH THAT TURNED
MY WORLD UPSIDE DOWN.

32:12.583 --> 32:14.959
IT'S BECAUSE FROM
THAT DAY FORWARD, I REALIZED

32:14.959 --> 32:17.458
THAT YOU HADN'T
BEEN MY FRIEND FOR...

32:17.458 --> 32:18.667
MAYBE QUITE SOME TIME,

32:18.667 --> 32:20.834
'CAUSE THE SECOND
YOU MADE US COMPETITORS--

32:20.834 --> 32:22.500
THAT I  MADE US COMPETITORS?

32:22.500 --> 32:24.250
NO. NO. NOW--NOW YOU'RE
REWRITING HISTORY, DAWSON.

32:24.250 --> 32:28.041
I REMEMBER WHEN
MY BEST FRIEND
HAD A CHOICE

32:28.041 --> 32:29.875
AND CHOSE
TO TURN HIS BACK ON ME.

32:29.875 --> 32:31.542
IF YOU'D EVER
STOPPED SETTIN' US UP
AGAINST EACH OTHER,

32:31.542 --> 32:34.583
YOU WOULDA REALIZED
THAT YOU AND I ARE
NOT THAT FAR APART.

32:34.583 --> 32:36.917
AH, SPARE ME THE SPEECH.
YOU ARE NOT GONNA CONVINCE ME

32:36.917 --> 32:39.083
THAT OUR WORLD'S...
ARE ANYTHING ALIKE.

32:39.083 --> 32:43.041
YOU'RE JUST UPSET
BECAUSE I BROKE OUTTA MINE.

32:43.041 --> 32:44.875
BROKE OUT OF YOURS? HOW?
BY PUTTING ON A SUIT

32:44.875 --> 32:46.458
AND SLAVIN' AWAY AT
SOMETHING THAT DOESN'T
EVEN INTEREST YOU?

32:46.458 --> 32:50.458
YOU MADE MONEY.
CONGRATULATIONS.
YOU IMPRESSED US ALL.

32:50.458 --> 32:52.834
HOW DARE YOU.
YOU KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT ME, MAN.

32:52.834 --> 32:55.458
I WAS GOOD  AT MY JOB.

32:55.458 --> 32:56.458
THEN WHY AM I BROKE?

32:56.458 --> 32:57.125
BECAUSE THAT'S LIFE!

32:57.125 --> 33:00.083
I DIDN'T MAKE THAT CHOICE!

33:00.083 --> 33:02.792
I HAVE LOST,
LITERALLY, EVERYTHING!

33:02.792 --> 33:04.792
WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM ME, MAN?

33:04.792 --> 33:06.625
DOES THIS MAKE YOU HAPPY,

33:06.625 --> 33:08.500
THAT YOU'RE BACK
ON TOP NOW?

33:08.500 --> 33:09.792
I MEAN, YOU ALWAYS
LIKED IT BETTER
WHEN YOU WERE IN CHARGE,

33:09.792 --> 33:13.667
SO IS THIS WHAT YOU WANTED?
DOES THIS MAKE IT ALL RIGHT?

33:13.667 --> 33:17.708
YOU DON'T
WANNA KNOW ME, PACE.

33:17.708 --> 33:20.291
YOU WROTE ME OFF
A LONG TIME AGO.

33:20.291 --> 33:22.458
REALLY? REALLY?

33:22.458 --> 33:26.166
BACK WHEN WE WERE
THE BEST OF FRIENDS?
WHEN WE WERE BROTHERS?

33:26.166 --> 33:29.041
WAS I JUST OUTTA THE HOUSE
EVERY TIME YOU TRIED TO CALL ME
OVER THE LAST 3 YEARS?

33:29.041 --> 33:32.166
OK, CAN YOU GUYS
JUST STOP IT?

33:32.166 --> 33:36.458
I CAN'T STAND HERE
AND LISTEN TO YOU GUYS
DO THIS ANYMORE.

33:37.917 --> 33:41.959
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO LOSE YOUR MONEY.

33:41.959 --> 33:44.667
