THAT THAT WOULD HAPPEN.

33:44.667 --> 33:46.792
I'M SORRY.

33:48.708 --> 33:51.041
YEAH, SO AM I.

33:51.041 --> 33:53.333
THIS--

33:55.000 --> 33:58.125
THIS WAS JUST A BIG MISTAKE
FROM THE BEGINNING, I GUESS.

33:59.667 --> 34:03.917
HEH. OK.

34:35.625 --> 34:37.667
YOU OK, PACE?

34:37.667 --> 34:39.291
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS.
DO WHAT?

34:41.542 --> 34:42.708
SIT OUT HERE WITH ME.

34:42.708 --> 34:45.208
I KNOW YOU'D RATHER BE
IN THE HOUSE WITH DAWSON,

34:45.208 --> 34:48.208
SO WHY DO YOU JUST GO
AND HELP HIM LICK HIS WOUNDS?

34:48.208 --> 34:50.458
THINGS NEVER CHANGE
HERE, DO THEY?

34:50.458 --> 34:51.708
NO...

34:51.708 --> 34:54.375
BECAUSE THESE ARE THE ROLES
WE WERE DESTINED TO PLAY.

34:54.375 --> 34:57.750
NO, PACE,
THESE ARE THE ROLES
WE CHOSE TO PLAY.

34:57.750 --> 35:00.083
I MEAN, LOOK AT US,

35:00.083 --> 35:02.625
SITTING OUT HERE
ON THIS DOCK IN FRONT
OF THE SAME HOUSE

35:02.625 --> 35:04.083
WE'VE BEEN HAUNTING
FOR YEARS.

35:04.083 --> 35:05.583
WE'RE PRACTICALLY GHOSTS
OF OUR FORMER SELVES,

35:05.583 --> 35:09.417
AND HONESTLY,
I DON'T THINK ANYONE
REALLY REMEMBERS

35:09.417 --> 35:10.375
WHAT THEY'RE
MAD ABOUT ANYMORE.

35:10.375 --> 35:14.166
MM, I WOULDN'T
BE SO SURE ABOUT THAT.

35:16.542 --> 35:18.417
PACEY, IF I WANTED TO GO
BACK INTO THAT HOUSE,

35:18.417 --> 35:21.083
