A LONG TIME AGO.

35:21.083 --> 35:23.417
DON'T YOU KNOW ME
AT ALL BY NOW?

35:23.417 --> 35:25.792
WELL, I DON'T
WANT YOU SITTING HERE
FEELING SORRY FOR ME.

35:25.792 --> 35:29.166
I DON'T
FEEL SORRY FOR YOU.
I FEEL  FOR YOU, PACEY.

35:29.166 --> 35:30.291
(SIGHS)

35:30.291 --> 35:32.291
GOD, CAN'T YOU EVER
TELL THE DIFFERENCE?

35:32.291 --> 35:33.458
I DON'T KNOW.

35:33.458 --> 35:34.458
(SIGHS)

35:34.458 --> 35:36.125
I DON'T KNOW,
BECAUSE YOU AND I HAVE HAD

35:36.125 --> 35:39.333
