OF THINGS.

35:39.333 --> 35:39.750
ESPECIALLY LATELY.

35:39.750 --> 35:42.291
(SCOFFS)

35:42.291 --> 35:43.333
OK.

35:43.333 --> 35:46.291
YOU KNOW, AND NO MATTER
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOU

35:46.291 --> 35:47.792
