I STAY WITH YOU,

35:47.792 --> 35:49.125
YOU'RE ONLY GONNA
REMEMBER THE MOMENTS
WHEN I LEAVE.

35:49.125 --> 35:52.166
WELL, YOU GOTTA
GIVE ME THAT MUCH,

35:52.166 --> 35:56.625
BECAUSE THOSE ARE PRETTY MUCH
THE MOST PAINFUL
MOMENTS IN MY LIFE.

35:56.625 --> 35:58.583
THAT'S BECAUSE YOU
ASK FOR THEM, PACEY.

35:58.583 --> 35:59.959
I'M SORRY. YOU DO.

35:59.959 --> 36:03.291
YOUR WHOLE LIFE,
YOU SPEND SO MUCH TIME
EXPECTING THE WORST

36:03.291 --> 36:06.792
THAT YOU DON'T EVEN
NOTICE THE MOMENTS WHEN
PEOPLE ARE LOVING YOU,

36:06.792 --> 36:09.542
AND, PACEY, PEOPLE
SPEND A LOT OF TIME
LOVING YOU.

36:09.542 --> 36:11.041
WELL...

36:11.041 --> 36:13.333
WITH ALL DUE RESPECT, JO,

36:13.333 --> 36:17.834
MY BEST FRIEND
JUST WALKED AWAY FROM ME,

36:17.834 --> 36:19.375
BUT THAT'S NOT EVEN
THE WORST OF IT.

36:19.375 --> 36:22.875
THE WORST THING IS
HE HASN'T EVEN REALLY KNOWN ME
FOR THE LAST 3 YEARS,

36:22.875 --> 36:24.166
SO PLEASE,
CLARIFY THAT FOR ME.

36:24.166 --> 36:26.667
HOW DOES THAT QUALIFY ME
AS A MAN WITH A SUPPORT NETWORK?

36:26.667 --> 36:29.917
WELL, YOU HAVE A PERSON
SITTING RIGHT HERE,
DON'T YOU?

36:29.917 --> 36:32.542
BUT OF COURSE,
THAT'S NOT ENOUGH.

36:32.542 --> 36:34.000
NOT UNTIL YOU LET IT.

36:34.000 --> 36:34.792
IN WHAT WORLD
DO I HAVE YOU?

36:34.792 --> 36:37.333
LOOK,

36:37.333 --> 36:39.291
JUST BECAUSE I DON'T
FIT INTO THAT...

36:39.291 --> 36:40.542
PLACE  YOU WANT ME TO

36:40.542 --> 36:42.875
DOESN'T MEAN THERE'S NOT
A PLACE FOR ME, PACEY.

36:42.875 --> 36:45.458
(SIGHS)

36:45.458 --> 36:48.250
DOES IT?

36:48.250 --> 36:50.500
JOEY, THIS ISN'T
YOUR FIGHT, ANYWAY.

36:50.500 --> 36:52.000
YOU'RE RIGHT.

36:52.000 --> 36:53.875
YOU'RE RIGHT.
IT'S NOT MY FIGHT

36:53.875 --> 36:55.208
BECAUSE
IT'S BEEN OVER

36:55.208 --> 36:57.917
FOR A REALLY
LONG TIME, PACEY,

36:57.917 --> 36:59.166
(SIGHS)

36:59.166 --> 37:01.792
AND IT IS UP TO YOU
TO MAKE IT RIGHT.

37:03.375 --> 37:05.458
I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO MAKE IT RIGHT.

37:05.458 --> 37:10.083
WELL, YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO FIGURE IT OUT.

37:10.083 --> 37:14.542
YOU KNOW, THAT'S
THE THING ABOUT GHOSTS.

37:14.542 --> 37:17.125
THEY SAY THAT...
THEY DON'T LEAVE

37:17.125 --> 37:19.917
UNTIL THEY'RE
AT PEACE WITH WHAT
THEY LEFT UNDONE.

37:25.208 --> 37:27.041
(CHUCKLES)

37:28.583 --> 37:29.417
HEY.

37:32.083 --> 37:33.375
SO...

37:33.375 --> 37:34.250
I GUESS
ANY PETTY BICKERING

37:34.250 --> 37:36.792
ABOUT WHEN YOU
WERE GONNA TELL ME

37:36.792 --> 37:38.083
IS PRETTY MUCH
OUTTA THE QUESTION
AT THIS POINT?

37:38.083 --> 37:40.500
OH, PLEASE. YOU KNOW
I LOVE BEMOANING
AFTER THE FACT.

37:40.500 --> 37:42.417
JEN, YOU JUST--
YOU GOTTA REALIZE

37:42.417 --> 37:44.250
THAT, YOU KNOW,
YOU AND GRAMS

37:44.250 --> 37:46.333
ARE PRETTY MUCH
ALL THE FAMILY
THAT I'VE GOT.

37:46.333 --> 37:48.750
I KNOW.

37:48.750 --> 37:51.041
DO YOU REMEMBER
THAT TIME THAT I WENT
OVER TO YOUR HOUSE

37:51.041 --> 37:52.083
AFTER GRAMS KICKED ME OUT?

37:52.083 --> 37:53.333
YEAH,
HOW COULD I FORGET?

37:53.333 --> 37:54.792
THAT'S THE DAY
YOU BECAME MY HAG.

37:54.792 --> 37:57.250
NO.

37:57.250 --> 38:00.667
NO, WE'RE FAMILY.
IT DOESN'T CHANGE.

38:02.333 --> 38:05.750
