IF YOU MAKE ME CRY TONIGHT.

38:05.750 --> 38:06.917
GRAMS...

38:06.917 --> 38:09.583
I'M SO SORRY.

38:09.583 --> 38:11.083
JACK...

38:11.083 --> 38:13.917
DON'T FEEL SORRY
FOR ME. JUST...

38:13.917 --> 38:15.792
BELIEVE IN ME, HMM?

38:15.792 --> 38:17.625
THAT'S  WHAT I NEED.

38:17.625 --> 38:20.500
WELL, I PROMISE
THAT I WILL COME
AND SEE THE TWO OF YOU

38:20.500 --> 38:22.083
EVERY CHANCE THAT I GET.

38:22.083 --> 38:23.917
OH, THAT WON'T
BE NECESSARY.

38:23.917 --> 38:26.333
OK.

38:26.333 --> 38:28.083
WELL, I MEAN,
YOU DON'T HONESTLY BELIEVE
JENNIFER AND I

38:28.083 --> 38:31.458
ARE GONNA LEAVE YOU
TO YOUR OWN QUESTIONABLE
DEVICES, DO YOU?

38:31.458 --> 38:32.834
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

38:32.834 --> 38:33.834
WHAT?

38:33.834 --> 38:35.542
