SIMPLY RATTLING AROUND

38:35.542 --> 38:37.834
THAT BIG HOUSE SHE GOT
THROUGH THE DIVORCE,

38:37.834 --> 38:42.625
AND I THINK WE NEED
A MAN AROUND THE HOUSE.

38:42.625 --> 38:46.208
I MEAN, YOU'LL HAVE TO SHARE
A ROOM WITH JENNIFER--

38:46.208 --> 38:48.792
OK, GRAMS, COME ON.
I MEAN, I--I--I JUST
CAN'T, YOU KNOW,

38:48.792 --> 38:51.041
PICK UP AND--
AND LEAVE THIS PLACE.

38:51.041 --> 38:52.708
COME ON, GUYS,
I HAVE STUFF...

38:52.708 --> 38:54.792
GOING ON, YOU KNOW?
AND I MEAN, BESIDES,
WHAT AM I GONNA DO,

38:54.792 --> 38:56.959
MOOCH OFF THE TWO
OF YOU FOR THE REST
OF OUR LIVES?

38:56.959 --> 38:59.083
CERTAINLY NOT.
YOU'LL BE EARNING YOUR KEEP.

38:59.083 --> 39:00.667
I MEAN, WHAT'S REALLY
KEEPING YOU HERE, JACK?

39:00.667 --> 39:02.166
YES, WHAT'S REALLY
KEEPING YOU HERE, JACK?

