LAST I HEARD, BEANTOWN
HAD NO GREAT HOLD ON YOU.

39:05.333 --> 39:07.166
Jen: YOU CAN BE
AN APATHETIC STUDENT
ANYWHERE,

39:07.166 --> 39:08.417
AND BOSTON BAY SUCKS.

39:08.417 --> 39:10.667
