WE HAVE A GIRL WHO'S
NEAR AND DEAR TO MY HEART

40:04.291 --> 40:06.500
OR AT LEAST ACROSS
FROM MY BEDROOM WINDOW.

40:06.500 --> 40:09.542
IF I HAD TO BE A WOMAN,
I'D BE AUDREY LIDDELL.

40:09.542 --> 40:10.250
